Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.08,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(648,484)}A marinha enfurecida {usado do mangá espanhol 845 título}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:38.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você realmente vai esperar por ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos em pleno território inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou esperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:53.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pound disse que aqueles que\N derrotam um general doce...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:57.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...acabam sendo derrotados em um instante...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:00.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...pelo exército vingativo de Big Mom, que é acompanhado por uma tempestade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então o inimigo virá...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:05.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji virá!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:11.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou esperar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:21.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minha cabeça foi cortada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há pouco o sol brilhava e \Nde repente nuvens de trovão...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo, Kingbaum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:47.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aquela montanha é o Whole Cake\N Château, onde mama vive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama está brava-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é possível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:09.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse é o poder de uma única pessoa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:17.09,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Linlin está acompanhada pelo clima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:22.18,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ninguém pode deter Big Mom\N quando ela fica brava.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.21,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1148,380)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(250,250)}SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:46.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prometheus-sama e Zeus-sama \Nestão causando estragos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama está furiosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O exército enfurecido está passando!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um exército foi formado\N para vingar Cracker-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está atrapalhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São muitos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:14.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que estão indo atrás de\N Chapéu de Palha para matá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:24.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano, ele disse que te esperaria lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse cara já está acabado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É Bobbin, o Economizador!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Amande, a Dama Demoníaca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mont-d'Or, o Escrivão!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:47.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quanto será a recompensa deles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.73,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,811)}Vou te esperar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, acho que esse capitão\N não é tão idiota...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...para não fugir ao ver essas tropas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está chovendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, é xarope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar esse xarope\N passar pela minha boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:55.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só vou comer a comida do Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.33,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(250,250)}WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, é a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão se comportando?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Anana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O chef não quer me\N emprestar uma faca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero cortar meu bichinho de pelúcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:32.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Dolce, Dragee, vão buscar uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se dermos uma faca a ela,\N ela vai estourar nossos balões!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela é má!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um dia vou matá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:46.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês não devem dizer\N esse tipo de coisa, né, mama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:53.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos têm cem ou duzentas\N pessoas que querem matar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se deem bem, meus filhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:08:00.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Amanhã será o casamento da Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que emocionante, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:09.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês poderão comer um delicioso bolo de casamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viva, viva!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.01,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Viva, viva!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, vamos nos reunir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com a família do noivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:20.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1766)}Porta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom que vocês vieram, Germa 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpem o atraso.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.57,Pensante,,0,0,0,,É Big Mom, a Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:40.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Houve um problema, mas já está tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você veio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpem o atraso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ouvi muitas histórias sobre ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seu filho é um cozinheiro, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o noivo perfeito para Pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, mesmo que não fosse, não importaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Porque é um casamento político.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:23.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto nossos interesses forem os mesmos,\N o resto não importa, Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:31.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas nada supera\N a felicidade de nossos filhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pela cerimônia de amanhã!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, vamos brindar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá verde!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:00.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá verde!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Qual você quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.68,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Qual você quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:06.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto, chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.34,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto, chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto, chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.60,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto, chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.08,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Comam-nos, comam-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:20.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Primeiro eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Comam-nos, comam-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também estou aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem muito mel, jovem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.56,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,É o melhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.53,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:34.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,La, la, la, almoço! La, la, la, almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:34.14,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,La, la, la, almoço! La, la, la, almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,La, la, la, almoço! La, la, la, almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.68,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,La, la, la, almoço! La, la, la, almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:37.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Salsicha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:38.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Repolho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:38.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Presunto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Panquecas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.92,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês poderiam ficar quietos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.46,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não diga isso e aproveite...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...um almoço divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:56.64,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,La, la, la, almoço! La, la, la, almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:56.64,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,La, la, la, almoço! La, la, la, almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:59.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que refeição barulhenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou delicioso?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2670,3170)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2670,3170)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2670,3170)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2670,3170)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2670,3170)}Vamos conversar em particular mais tarde.
Comment: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,Note,,0,0,0,,I NEED TO TALK TO YOU IN PRIVATE LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.26,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(250,250)}NOS ARREDORES DE SWEET CITY {tradução do mangá espanhol 845}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.09,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(250,250)}Equipe Luffy {Traduzido por mim}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não-ju...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:10.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como podem ser tantos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos se esconda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vai acontecer nada se você se afastar\N um pouco daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji pode chegar a qualquer momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:52.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É inútil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você sabe em que território estamos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse exército...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não vai conseguir derrotá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Encontramos o Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu prometi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...que o esperaria aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.06,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(250,250)}DENTRO DO WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU {tradução do mangá espanhol 845}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,650,,Você guiou Luffy e os outros para esta ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prometi que te levaria para a costa sudoeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.31,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1146,415)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(250,250)}QUARTO \NDA PUDDING
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:06.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas não consegui e acabei\N colocando todos em apuros.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:15.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Achei estranho que conseguissem navegar\N por um mar tão vigiado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de qualquer forma, eu não teria ido para aquela costa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:28.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você está preocupado com o convite,\N eu vou dizer que a culpa é minha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, se você for ao casamento, será o seu fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:36.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama está acostumada com casamentos políticos,\N então coloca braceletes nos noivos que podem fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você tentar sair da ilha com eles...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles explodirão.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua mama tem a chave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:51.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para conseguir, teríamos que derrotar\N os Piratas da Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que mama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:15:00.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, ela já fez esses preparativos e, além disso,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,eu não tenho nenhum aliado.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Embora tenhamos o mesmo sangue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,é isso que eles fazem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:28.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi sua própria família que fez isso com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:38.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles me consideram um fracasso\N e não suportam minha existência...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:44.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nunca fui feliz por ter nascido\N como parte da realeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso eu fui para o mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e me dirigi a um lugar distante e desconhecido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...se eu me opuser a este casamento,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,eles vão matar todos os meus companheiros.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E não só isso,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:15.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,também vão matar no East Blue o meu salvador,\N a quem considero meu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:20.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma que eu olhe, não há saída.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Decidi parar de resistir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como condição para aceitar este casamento,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,quero que Big Mom deixe\N meus companheiros irem embora! {SC810 13:59:13}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles foram atrás de Luffy e os outros.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:54.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minha mama te encurralou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é sua culpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:08.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até treze anos atrás, eu vivia no inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Simplesmente voltei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:17.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fui feliz por estar longe do\N inferno por treze anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,As pessoas que me ajudaram a melhorar\N minhas habilidades de cozinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e os companheiros com quem viajei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devo muito a todos eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:32.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero desaparecer sem machucar ninguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:38.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minha aventura termina aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:47.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, não chore, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você me faz sentir mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:02.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou permitir que nosso\N casamento seja um inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que estou dizendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está sofrendo muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:20.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um casamento indesejado\N deve ser um inferno, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:23.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não deveria ter dito isso enquanto você está sofrendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou envergonhada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós nos conhecemos há pouco tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não posso preencher o vazio\N que há no seu coração!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:37.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para começar, você nunca\N disse que se casaria comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é minha salvação.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se eu parecer bom o suficiente para você,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,vamos nos casar amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por todos os danos.... {linha em inglês: "Thanks for all the damage."}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.32,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(456,0)}NOS ARREDORES DE SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Venha aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me descuidei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:20:01.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pensei que uma garota pudesse\N criar um raio tão grande.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meitou,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Shirauo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.05,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2590,3090)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.05,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2590,3090)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.05,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2590,3090)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.05,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2590,3090)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.05,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2590,3090)}Peixe de gelo asiático.
Comment: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.05,Note,,0,0,0,,Icefish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é assim-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós não a traímos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Amande-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Slow Ballad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.44,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.44,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.44,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.44,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.44,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Balada lenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:06.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:11.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Se vai fazer isso, faça rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:18.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para que matar se vai ser rápido?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:23.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu corto na velocidade que\N causa mais dor e tormento.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não posso acreditar, Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:41.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não parece que ele ficou lutando contra o Big Bro Cracker a noite toda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:44.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os soldados de xadrez não são fracos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você os derrota como se fossem lixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:53.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, venha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:03.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cream Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.40,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,3130,3630)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.40,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,3130,3630)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.40,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3130,3630)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.40,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3130,3630)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.40,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,3130,3630)}Monstro de creme. {SC810 9:01}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:14.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:18.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse é o poder da doçura\N do creme fresco-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando meu creme doce se adoça,\N todo o seu corpo queima-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:32.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no... {SC811 8:14}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:35.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vai funcionar, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde estou?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:25.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:29.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...o mundo dos livros!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Q-Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:40.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cream Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:48.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:15.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:16.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esquiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.52,0:24:26.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2700,3200)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2700,3200)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2700,3200)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2700,3200)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:24:31.50,0:24:33.90,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2700,3200)}Golpe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Soco!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,...Soco!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.40,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}...de creme.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.40,0:24:41.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Luffy!
Comment: 0,0:24:45.16,0:24:46.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não... {linha extra}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.91,0:25:05.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum... {SC811 17:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.16,0:25:23.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me perguntava por que os soldados de xadrez, que são homies, não lutavam bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.18,0:25:27.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e por que conseguiram sair\N da floresta de confusão.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:29.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:33.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como você tem o\N Cartão de Vida da mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.67,0:25:36.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está escrito o nome de Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.13,0:25:37.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.74,0:25:39.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você roubou dela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:40.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas que terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.68,0:25:42.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês mataram a garota que fugiu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.68,0:25:43.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.86,0:25:44.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que ela disse antes de morrer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.98,0:25:46.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão enganados!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.26,0:25:47.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lola é minha amiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.82,0:25:48.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela me deu isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.85,0:25:50.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Duvido.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:52.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conte isso para a mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.42,0:25:56.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, recebemos ordens\N para capturá-los vivos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.03,0:25:57.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.11,0:26:00.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, vejam o que fizeram...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.58,0:26:04.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram quase todos\N os soldados de xadrez.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:30.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu... {esta linha e a próxima tiveram que ser misturadas de linhas canônicas/não canônicas}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:33.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou esperar aqui...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.31,0:26:41.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.11,0:26:50.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.51,0:27:08.52,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(519,0)}WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.54,0:27:14.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.33,0:27:17.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.19,0:27:23.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou muito sensata quando se\N trata de acordos razoáveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.25,0:27:25.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou deixar seus companheiros,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.34,0:27:29.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,os Piratas do Chapéu\N de Palha, deixarem a ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.56,0:27:32.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu prometo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.29,0:27:39.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você se resignar a ficar aqui e se casar,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.19,0:27:42.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,eu vou ignorar muitas coisas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:44.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.04,0:27:47.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aconteça o que acontecer, vou\N fazer a Pudding-chan feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.16,0:27:54.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, você se apaixonou pela minha filha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.74,0:27:57.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que alegria!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.11,0:28:02.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me te dizer uma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.42,0:28:09.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Normalmente, eu não perdoaria o que\N os Chapéus de Palha fizeram comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.12,0:28:18.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles destruíram a floresta de confusão\N e derrotaram um general doce.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.50,0:28:23.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, na Ilha dos Homens-Peixe,\N eles comeram meus doces...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.87,0:28:26.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e me desafiaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.93,0:28:35.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas agora minha prioridade é o seu casamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.21,0:28:37.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se tudo correr bem,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:42.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,amanhã a esta hora eu terei\N obtido o poder militar de Germa...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.44,0:28:50.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e todos nós comeremos um\N delicioso bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.82,0:28:58.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você não fugir, tudo será\N resolvido pacificamente, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.29,0:29:00.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.93,0:29:15.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Dizem que...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.94,0:29:21.92,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(513,0)}SALA DO TESOURO DO WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.94,0:29:19.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...em todo o mundo há trinta Poneglyphs,{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.84,0:29:25.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,inscritos em rochas que nunca\N foram quebradas...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.33,0:29:28.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...em centenas de anos-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.75,0:29:39.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E apenas nove desses trinta\N Poneglyphs contêm informações. {Linha original: "And only nine of those 30 Poneglyphs have specific kinds of information", significado um pouco diferente}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.00,0:29:43.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você os levar para Laugh Tale, a última ilha,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.62,0:29:49.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,as pedras contarão a verdade\N sobre este mundo-soir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.35,0:29:54.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare, por favor, \NSmoothie-sama, general doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.52,0:29:56.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por favor, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:59.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Piedade, Smoothie-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.24,0:30:11.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Smoothie-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.12,0:30:20.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas, para chegar a Laugh Tale, a última ilha,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.91,0:30:24.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,são necessários os quatro\N Road Poneglyphs, as pedras vermelhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.67,0:30:29.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Contando o que Jinbe trouxe\N no outro dia,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.47,0:30:31.34,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Um presente.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.34,0:30:32.97,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Peguei no meu caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.97,0:30:34.27,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Também é meu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.27,0:30:40.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,nós, os Piratas da Big Mom,\N temos dois Poneglyphs...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.19,0:30:43.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e um Road Poneglyph!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:47.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No total, temos três pedras-vous plaít.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.74,0:30:52.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sei que essas três pedras são importantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.87,0:30:56.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.83,0:31:01.56,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,475)\fad(513,251)}PIRATAS DA BIG MOM
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.83,0:31:01.56,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(525,251)}"GENERAL DOCE" (MINISTRA DOS SUCOS)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:31:01.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você reforçou a segurança\N tão repentinamente, Tamago?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.20,0:31:03.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não tenho nada para fazer\N até a festa do chá.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.83,0:31:06.78,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,475)\fad(513,0)}14ª FILHA DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE - SMOOTHIE
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.83,0:31:06.78,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(513,0)}RECOMPENSA: 932 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.66,0:31:06.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então não me importo\N de ajudar a reforçar a segurança.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:11.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, obrigado-renaissance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.01,0:31:17.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há cinco anos, um ex-capitão pirata\N veio a esta ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.22,0:31:20.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é um mink e um ladrão de Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.36,0:31:26.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E, aparentemente, ele se infiltrou\N novamente nesta ilha-souffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.10,0:31:32.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua vida foi poupada a pedido\N de Pekoms, seu compatriota.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.22,0:31:35.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que ele está nos desafiando novamente?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.20,0:31:39.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:49.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você pode chegar a Laugh Tale se\N conseguir os quatro Road Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.30,0:31:52.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ou seja, é o caminho\N para se tornar o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.28,0:31:57.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São objetos pelos quais\N os Yonkou competem-bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.85,0:32:09.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Daremos nossas vidas para proteger até o fim\N esses trunfos-chocolat!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:18.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(485,0)}AO LADO DA SALA DO TESOURO DO WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.21,0:32:23.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:29.05,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(485,0)}ADEGA DE VINHOS
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.05,0:32:30.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.08,0:32:31.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aumentaram a segurança?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.97,0:32:36.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, havia uma pessoa chamada\N Smoothie, uma general doce.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.75,0:32:38.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,General doce...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.26,0:32:39.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um alto comando!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.93,0:32:41.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi o que pensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.76,0:32:43.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso ela parecia tão forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.74,0:32:45.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não temos esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.67,0:32:48.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles têm uma segurança impecável.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.30,0:32:51.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há pontos fracos, nem à noite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.54,0:32:57.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,As esperanças acabaram\N quando Tamago me identificou.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.67,0:33:00.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Justo quando Luffy e os outros\N estão sofrendo tanto...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.69,0:33:04.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem dera pudéssemos completar\N nossa missão facilmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.08,0:33:10.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No outro dia, fiquei emocionado com o que você disse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.89,0:33:15.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para que Luffy-san se torne o Rei dos Piratas,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.14,0:33:19.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,algum dia ele precisará dos Road Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.81,0:33:24.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas será muito complicado voltar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.81,0:33:30.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, teríamos que lutar de frente\N contra eles se quiséssemos voltar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.98,0:33:33.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas duvido que possamos chegar\N até este lugar assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.08,0:33:36.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.57,0:33:41.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, esta pode ser uma\N oportunidade única.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.41,0:33:47.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas se atacarmos de frente,\N nós dois morreremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.75,0:33:51.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é o alvo do Barão Tamago?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.64,0:33:53.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.51,0:34:06.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pedro-san, você poderia ser a isca?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.20,0:34:14.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o mesmo que eu estava pensando.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.32,0:34:17.23,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTiming:\NHalee,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inquebráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e acene...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inquebráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}nós já decidimos há muito tempo.
